text: And geond eall þæt hus singe man þasVIIsealmas,Domine ne in furoresemel,Beati quorum, Domine ne in furorebis,Miserere mei, deus, Inclina domine, Domine exaudisemel,De profundis, Domine exaudibis, and þa letanias.
And gif man fyrstes hæbbe, þonne ræde man Cristes þrowunge and oðre halige bec, þæt þær sy symble buton tolætednesse sealmsang oððe haligra boca ræding.
And singe man þysne <responsorium>, gif þe þince, þæt he his gast agifen hæbbe his drihtne, þe hine gesceop and geworhte.
